{"type": "article", "id": 4695, "title": "Joseph Joseph 砧板套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-25T08:01:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233509MkQotUS6YA4PsJpE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国厨房餐具设计品牌 Joseph Joseph 推出了一套砧板套装，为了避免不同食物类型的细菌感染，将其分为 4 类，分别提供海鲜、熟食、肉类以及蔬菜的红白蓝绿 4 色砧板，做到生熟分开，真正为人体的健康着想，其银色套装盒子的下方还做了特别的滤水功能设计，以便于用户随时清洗完砧板将其收纳，方便实用。定价 48 英镑（约合人民币 463 元），<a href=\"http://www.josephjoseph.com/product/index-chopping-boards\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233507LKXY5rWQyIju0iUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335085FIKWOUMCDjgGm6z.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335089EQW7256cognX0bG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}